fulltitle: The CIA & Jonestown: Interview with aide to Congressman Ryan (1980)
title: The CIA & Jonestown: Interview with aide to Congressman Ryan (1980)
_filename: _The CIA & Jonestown - Interview with aide to Congressman Ryan (1980).mp4
description:
Though the aides testimony to the US Congress is still classified some 35 years later, we do have this brief clip in which he links Jonestown to CIA operatives and CIA mind control experiments like MKULTRA.

Congressional Report on Jonestown and the murder of Leo J. Ryan: https://archive.org/details/AssassinationOfLeoRyanAndJonestownTragedy
More on MKULTRA: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HeWb-Har7uo
More on Human Experimentation by the US Government: https://archive.org/details/US-Government-Medical-Experimentation-On-Humans

Pulled from the documentary "Evidence of Revision Part 5: Jonestown and MKULTRA". The music is in the film.

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
